title: Ep 30: Dumper to Dumper
description:
Today's proceedings: We welcome new listeners from Headgum's "If I Were You" as we deliberate over a man accidentally finding a new fetish, a woman having and unplanned bathroom break, a toothless first kiss, and a man who accidentally gained a murder of crow bodyguards.  Also, in this week's Circle Jurdge, Josh calls out Christian for last week's Circle Jurdge fiasco.
